<p>Howdy! I stumbled upon the Foundation a few years ago via a simple google search. (Who would've thought?) Since then, the Foundation has endlessly inspired me and I regularly discuss it with the handful of fellow skippers I know in real life. I'm so grateful that I actually took the time to become a member.</p>
<p>Currently, I plan to read, comment, vote and–when I have a little more experience under my belt–review. Me and my friend (who, despite my best efforts, is not yet a member of this site) have an idea for an SCP in the works, but it's still in the very early stages.</p>
<p>For the monthly question: I often lay awake at night, pondering my future career. Also, I must confess that I have a habit of watching SCP Illustrated immediately before bed, and I'm sure you can imagine how that turned out.</p>
<p>Overall, I am extremely happy and proud to call myself a member of this amazing site! See you around!</p>

